channel.title: Hamachi is booked.[READ] if your having hamachi problems
channel.description:
[size=15pt][u][b]Hamachi Problems[/b][/u][/size]
_______________________________________________________________________________
[b]Server reported that it is currently experiencing a high volume of connection request and therefore can not accept your connection at the moment.[/b]
[b]DO NOT:[/b]Post anymore Topics about not being able to connect to server.
Hamachi is down because of so many people connecting. :mad:
If you cannot log into hamachi or are getting errors post here.
___________________________________________________________________________
[u][size=15pt][b]To Download Hamachi[/b][/size][/u]
For hamachi go here --> [url=http://www.hamachi.cc/]http://www.hamachi.cc/[/url]
After thats downloaded click Create or join networks.
For creatng a network you should be the one running the server.
Enter the name of networks that relates to your servers name. [b]Example[/b] Testscape1 Testscape2 Testscape3
Pass- test
For joining a server's hamachi network. "Join Network"
Then enter the Hamachi name that it tells you.
Enter the password it says.
[b]Example[/b] !TestScape!
[u]Hamachi Networks[/u] Testscape1 Testscape2 Testscape3
Pass- test
